'''Jamie Glover''' was the voice of [[General/Legends|General]] [[Maximilian Veers/Legends|Maximilian Veers]] in ''[[Star Wars: Battlefront II]]'' and in ''[[Star Wars: Empire at War]]''. He also did voice work in [[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords|''Knights of the Old Republic II'']] as [[Azkul]], ''[[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II]]'' as an Imperial Officer, and ''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]'' as [[Darth Malgus]].

His father, [[Julian Glover]], played [[General/Legends|General]] [[Maximilian Veers/Legends|Maximilian Veers]] in [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''The Empire Strikes Back'']].<ref name="Insider113">{{InsiderCite|113|The Sacking of Coruscant}}</ref>

